data.description: This property is the epitome of country living, and truly has it all! On just shy of 6 acres, this 5 bed, 2 bath, 2720 sqft farmhouse with a wrap around porch has been beautifully updated with LVP flooring, new appliances, interior and exterior paint, still leaving you the opportunity to add your personal touches. There is ample storage for all of your toys and equipment in the 30x30 shop, plenty of space and shelter for your horses and/or cows with 2 separate pastures and a beautiful barn complete with 5 stalls, and tack room. It does not stop there- this property is also equipped with an oversized chicken coop, brand new greenhouse, and has its very own creek running through the property year around. The beauty, privacy, and serenity that this property encompasses is unmatched!
